{
  "video_id": "sRT61YB0hSQ",
  "title": "How do you build a sacred space? | Siamak Hariri",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12645.0,
      "end_time": 16975.0,
      "text": "The school of architecture that I studied at some 30 years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16999.0,
      "end_time": 20837.0,
      "text": "happened to be across the street from the wonderful art gallery"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20862.0,
      "end_time": 24490.0,
      "text": "designed by the great architect Louis Kahn."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24977.0,
      "end_time": 28690.0,
      "text": "I love the building, and I used to visit it quite often."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 28714.0,
      "end_time": 30244.0,
      "text": "One day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30269.0,
      "end_time": 35364.0,
      "text": "I saw the security guard run his hand across the concrete wall."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 36852.0,
      "end_time": 38583.0,
      "text": "And it was the way he did it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 38608.0,
      "end_time": 40342.0,
      "text": "the expression on his face --"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 41254.0,
      "end_time": 43876.0,
      "text": "something touched me."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43901.0,
      "end_time": 48426.0,
      "text": "I could see that the security guard was moved by the building"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 49511.0,
      "end_time": 53649.0,
      "text": "and that architecture has that capacity"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 53673.0,
      "end_time": 54835.0,
      "text": "to move you."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 55349.0,
      "end_time": 57775.0,
      "text": "I could see it, and I remember thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 57800.0,
      "end_time": 62250.0,
      "text": "\"Wow. How does architecture do that?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 63175.0,
      "end_time": 67351.0,
      "text": "At school, I was learning to design,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 67375.0,
      "end_time": 70437.0,
      "text": "but here -- here was a reaction of the heart."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 71779.0,
      "end_time": 75630.0,
      "text": "And it touched me to the core."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 77349.0,
      "end_time": 81796.0,
      "text": "You know, you aspire for beauty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 83130.0,
      "end_time": 88241.0,
      "text": "for sensuousness, for atmosphere, the emotional response."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 89550.0,
      "end_time": 92820.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the realm of the ineffable"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 92106.0,
      "end_time": 93877.0,
      "text": "and the immeasurable."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 93901.0,
      "end_time": 96420.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s what you live for:"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 96791.0,
      "end_time": 98426.0,
      "text": "a chance to try."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 99678.0,
      "end_time": 103155.0,
      "text": "So in 2003, there was an open call for designs"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 103179.0,
      "end_time": 105301.0,
      "text": "for the Bahá&#39;í Temple for South America."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 105325.0,
      "end_time": 108323.0,
      "text": "This was the first temple in all of South America."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 108347.0,
      "end_time": 110231.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a continental temple,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 110255.0,
      "end_time": 113434.0,
      "text": "a hugely important milestone for the Bahá&#39;í community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 113458.0,
      "end_time": 117690.0,
      "text": "because this would be the last of the continental temples"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 117714.0,
      "end_time": 121270.0,
      "text": "and would open the door for national and local temples to be built"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 121294.0,
      "end_time": 122619.0,
      "text": "around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 122643.0,
      "end_time": 126193.0,
      "text": "And the brief was deceptively simple"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 126217.0,
      "end_time": 129865.0,
      "text": "and unique in the annals of religion:"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 130882.0,
      "end_time": 135864.0,
      "text": "a circular room, nine sides, nine entrances, nine paths,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 137856.0,
      "end_time": 143338.0,
      "text": "allowing you to come to the temple from all directions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 143362.0,
      "end_time": 146296.0,
      "text": "nine symbolizing completeness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 146320.0,
      "end_time": 147560.0,
      "text": "perfection."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 148346.0,
      "end_time": 151860.0,
      "text": "No pulpit, no sermons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 151884.0,
      "end_time": 154220.0,
      "text": "as there are no clergy in the Bahá&#39;í faith."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 154830.0,
      "end_time": 158935.0,
      "text": "And in a world which is putting up walls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 158959.0,
      "end_time": 162407.0,
      "text": "the design needed to express in form"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 162431.0,
      "end_time": 163716.0,
      "text": "the very opposite."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 164899.0,
      "end_time": 168847.0,
      "text": "It had to be open, welcoming"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 168871.0,
      "end_time": 173415.0,
      "text": "to people of all faiths, walks of life, backgrounds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 173439.0,
      "end_time": 175424.0,
      "text": "or no faith at all;"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 176163.0,
      "end_time": 179452.0,
      "text": "a new form of sacred space"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 179476.0,
      "end_time": 181490.0,
      "text": "with no pattern"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 182474.0,
      "end_time": 184998.0,
      "text": "or models to draw from."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 186148.0,
      "end_time": 190600.0,
      "text": "It was like designing one of the first churches for Christianity"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 190300.0,
      "end_time": 192712.0,
      "text": "or one of the first mosques for Islam."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 193869.0,
      "end_time": 198455.0,
      "text": "So we live in a secular world."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 200399.0,
      "end_time": 205442.0,
      "text": "How do you design sacred space today?"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 206118.0,
      "end_time": 210659.0,
      "text": "And how do you even define what&#39;s sacred today?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 212823.0,
      "end_time": 217797.0,
      "text": "I stumbled across this beautiful quote from the Bahá&#39;í writings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 217821.0,
      "end_time": 219629.0,
      "text": "and it speaks to prayer."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 221252.0,
      "end_time": 223361.0,
      "text": "It says that if you reach out in prayer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 224751.0,
      "end_time": 228495.0,
      "text": "and if your prayer is answered -- which is already very interesting --"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 228519.0,
      "end_time": 232949.0,
      "text": "that the pillars of your heart will become ashine."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 234116.0,
      "end_time": 236816.0,
      "text": "And I loved this idea of the inner and the outer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 237768.0,
      "end_time": 243118.0,
      "text": "like when you see someone and you say, \"That person is radiant.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 243999.0,
      "end_time": 249310.0,
      "text": "And I was thinking, \"My gosh, how could we make something"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 249550.0,
      "end_time": 251118.0,
      "text": "architectural out of that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 251142.0,
      "end_time": 255347.0,
      "text": "where you create a building"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 255371.0,
      "end_time": 258159.0,
      "text": "and it becomes alive with light?"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 259341.0,
      "end_time": 263359.0,
      "text": "Like alabaster, if you kiss it with light, it becomes alive."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 263384.0,
      "end_time": 265526.0,
      "text": "And I drew this sketch,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 265550.0,
      "end_time": 268911.0,
      "text": "something with two layers, translucent"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 268935.0,
      "end_time": 271692.0,
      "text": "with structure in between capturing light."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 272466.0,
      "end_time": 278427.0,
      "text": "Maybe a pure form, a single form of emanation"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 278451.0,
      "end_time": 280872.0,
      "text": "that you could imagine"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 280896.0,
      "end_time": 284400.0,
      "text": "would be all dome"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 284424.0,
      "end_time": 287895.0,
      "text": "and everything we kept making was looking too much like an egg."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 287919.0,
      "end_time": 289529.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 289553.0,
      "end_time": 290776.0,
      "text": "A blob."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 291526.0,
      "end_time": 292744.0,
      "text": "So you search."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 293349.0,
      "end_time": 297852.0,
      "text": "You all know this crazy search, letting the process take you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 297876.0,
      "end_time": 299500.0,
      "text": "and you live for the surprises."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 299524.0,
      "end_time": 301750.0,
      "text": "And I remember quite by accident"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 301774.0,
      "end_time": 307146.0,
      "text": "I saw this little video of a plant moving in light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 307170.0,
      "end_time": 310833.0,
      "text": "and it made me think of movement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 310857.0,
      "end_time": 312290.0,
      "text": "reach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 312530.0,
      "end_time": 314369.0,
      "text": "this idea that the temple could have reach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 314393.0,
      "end_time": 316164.0,
      "text": "like this reach for the divine."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 317227.0,
      "end_time": 319510.0,
      "text": "You can imagine also"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 319760.0,
      "end_time": 323971.0,
      "text": "that movement within a circle could mean movement and stillness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 323995.0,
      "end_time": 325986.0,
      "text": "like the cosmos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 326100.0,
      "end_time": 328654.0,
      "text": "something you see in many places."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 329705.0,
      "end_time": 332107.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 332131.0,
      "end_time": 335445.0,
      "text": "But rotation was not enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 336668.0,
      "end_time": 338852.0,
      "text": "because we needed a form."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 338876.0,
      "end_time": 341142.0,
      "text": "In the Bahá&#39;í writings, it talks about"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 341166.0,
      "end_time": 346280.0,
      "text": "the temples being as perfect as is humanly possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 346520.0,
      "end_time": 348629.0,
      "text": "and we kept thinking, well, what is perfection?"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 348653.0,
      "end_time": 352997.0,
      "text": "And I remember I stumbled into this image of this Japanese basket"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 353210.0,
      "end_time": 357220.0,
      "text": "and thinking our Western notions of perfection need to be challenged,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 357460.0,
      "end_time": 361769.0,
      "text": "that this wonderful silhouette of this basket, this wonkiness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 361793.0,
      "end_time": 367441.0,
      "text": "and that it has the kind of dimple of what you might imagine a shoulder"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 367465.0,
      "end_time": 368972.0,
      "text": "or the cheekbone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 368996.0,
      "end_time": 371128.0,
      "text": "and that kind of organic form."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 371873.0,
      "end_time": 374686.0,
      "text": "And so we drew and made models,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 374710.0,
      "end_time": 377924.0,
      "text": "these lines that merge at the top,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 377949.0,
      "end_time": 379287.0,
      "text": "soft lines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 380307.0,
      "end_time": 383248.0,
      "text": "which became like drapery"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 383272.0,
      "end_time": 386769.0,
      "text": "and translucent veils and folding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 386793.0,
      "end_time": 390883.0,
      "text": "and the idea of not only folding but torquing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 390907.0,
      "end_time": 393911.0,
      "text": "you remember the plant and the way it was reaching."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 394737.0,
      "end_time": 398376.0,
      "text": "And this started to become an interesting form,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 398400.0,
      "end_time": 401870.0,
      "text": "carving the base, making the entrances."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 401796.0,
      "end_time": 403919.0,
      "text": "And then we ended up with this."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 403943.0,
      "end_time": 407539.0,
      "text": "This is this temple with two layers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 407564.0,
      "end_time": 410570.0,
      "text": "nine luminous veils,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 410810.0,
      "end_time": 411556.0,
      "text": "embodied light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 411580.0,
      "end_time": 413527.0,
      "text": "soft-flowing lines"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 413551.0,
      "end_time": 415714.0,
      "text": "like luminescent drapery."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 415738.0,
      "end_time": 419807.0,
      "text": "180 submissions were received from 80 countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 419831.0,
      "end_time": 421838.0,
      "text": "and this was selected."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 421862.0,
      "end_time": 427490.0,
      "text": "So we went to the next stage of how to build it."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 427851.0,
      "end_time": 430705.0,
      "text": "We had submitted alabaster."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 431935.0,
      "end_time": 434465.0,
      "text": "But alabaster was too soft,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 434489.0,
      "end_time": 437965.0,
      "text": "and we were experimenting, many experiments with materials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 437989.0,
      "end_time": 441354.0,
      "text": "trying to think how we could have this kind of shimmer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 442412.0,
      "end_time": 445436.0,
      "text": "and we ended up with borosilicate."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 445460.0,
      "end_time": 449360.0,
      "text": "And borosilicate glass, as you know, is very strong,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 449600.0,
      "end_time": 454286.0,
      "text": "and if you break borosilicate rods just so and melt them"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 454310.0,
      "end_time": 456614.0,
      "text": "at just the right temperature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 456638.0,
      "end_time": 458405.0,
      "text": "we ended up with this new material,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 458430.0,
      "end_time": 462644.0,
      "text": "this new cast glass which took us about two years to make."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 463578.0,
      "end_time": 465881.0,
      "text": "And it had this quality that we loved,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 465905.0,
      "end_time": 467943.0,
      "text": "this idea of the embodied light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 468976.0,
      "end_time": 473306.0,
      "text": "but on the inside, we wanted something with a soft light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 473330.0,
      "end_time": 475941.0,
      "text": "like the inner lining of a jacket."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 475965.0,
      "end_time": 479863.0,
      "text": "On the outside you have protection, but on the inside you touch it."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 480625.0,
      "end_time": 486440.0,
      "text": "So we found this tiny vein in a huge quarry in Portugal"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 486464.0,
      "end_time": 489747.0,
      "text": "with this beautiful stone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 489771.0,
      "end_time": 494781.0,
      "text": "which the owner had kept for seven generations in his family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 494805.0,
      "end_time": 497666.0,
      "text": "waiting for the right project, if you can believe it."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 499697.0,
      "end_time": 501789.0,
      "text": "Look at this material, it&#39;s beautiful."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 501813.0,
      "end_time": 505151.0,
      "text": "And the way it lights up; it has that translucent quality."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 506224.0,
      "end_time": 508436.0,
      "text": "So here you see the structure."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 508993.0,
      "end_time": 510573.0,
      "text": "It lets the light through."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 511329.0,
      "end_time": 514991.0,
      "text": "And looking down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 515150.0,
      "end_time": 517287.0,
      "text": "the nine wings are bound,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 517311.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520851.00000000006,
      "text": "structurally but symbolically strong,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 520875.0,
      "end_time": 523250.0,
      "text": "a great symbol of unity:"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 524373.0,
      "end_time": 527446.0,
      "text": "pure geometry, a perfect circle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 527470.0,
      "end_time": 531856.0,
      "text": "30 meters in section and in plan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 531880.0,
      "end_time": 533660.0,
      "text": "perfectly symmetrical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 533684.0,
      "end_time": 536661.0,
      "text": "like the idea of sacredness and geometry."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 537812.0,
      "end_time": 540968.0,
      "text": "And here you see the building going up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 540992.0,
      "end_time": 543279.0,
      "text": "2,000 steel nodes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 543303.0,
      "end_time": 546326.0,
      "text": "9,000 pieces of steel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 547170.0,
      "end_time": 549805.0,
      "text": "7,800 stone pieces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 549829.0,
      "end_time": 554361.0,
      "text": "10,000 cast glass pieces, all individual shapes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 554385.0,
      "end_time": 557418.0,
      "text": "the entire superstructure all described,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 557442.0,
      "end_time": 561933.0,
      "text": "engineered, fabricated with aerospace technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 561957.0,
      "end_time": 565144.0,
      "text": "prefabricated machine to machine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 565168.0,
      "end_time": 567320.0,
      "text": "robotically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 567560.0,
      "end_time": 569333.0,
      "text": "a huge team effort, you can imagine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 569357.0,
      "end_time": 571300.0,
      "text": "of literally hundreds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 571325.0,
      "end_time": 576530.0,
      "text": "and within three percent of our $30 million budget"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 576770.0,
      "end_time": 578360.0,
      "text": "set in 2006."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 578384.0,
      "end_time": 580310.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 581901.0,
      "end_time": 586992.0,
      "text": "Nine wings bound together"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 587170.0,
      "end_time": 589188.0,
      "text": "forming a nine-pointed star,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 590760.0,
      "end_time": 594390.0,
      "text": "and the star shape moving in space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 595187.0,
      "end_time": 596665.0,
      "text": "tracking the sun."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 607582.0,
      "end_time": 609220.0,
      "text": "So here it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 609460.0,
      "end_time": 610819.0,
      "text": "Audience: Wow!"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 611621.0,
      "end_time": 616943.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 619806.0,
      "end_time": 624222.0,
      "text": "Hopefully, a befitting response to that beautiful quote,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 625206.0,
      "end_time": 627342.0,
      "text": "\"a prayer answered,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 627366.0,
      "end_time": 629696.0,
      "text": "open in all directions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 630593.0,
      "end_time": 632986.0,
      "text": "capturing the blue light of dawn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 634530.0,
      "end_time": 637736.0,
      "text": "tent-like white light of day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 637760.0,
      "end_time": 640678.0,
      "text": "the gold light of the afternoon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 640702.0,
      "end_time": 643484.0,
      "text": "and of course, at night, the reversal:"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 645302.0,
      "end_time": 646620.0,
      "text": "sensuous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 648191.0,
      "end_time": 651664.0,
      "text": "catching the light in all kinds of mysterious ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 653403.0,
      "end_time": 659140.0,
      "text": "And the site: it&#39;s interesting; 14 years ago when we made the submission,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 659380.0,
      "end_time": 661148.0,
      "text": "we showed the temple set against the Andes."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 661172.0,
      "end_time": 663882.0,
      "text": "We didn&#39;t have the Andes as our site,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 665525.0,
      "end_time": 668560.0,
      "text": "but after nine years, that&#39;s exactly where we ended up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 670347.0,
      "end_time": 673811.0,
      "text": "the lines of the temple set against nothing but pure nature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 673835.0,
      "end_time": 678974.0,
      "text": "and you turn around and you get nothing but the city below you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 678998.0,
      "end_time": 683686.0,
      "text": "and inside, a view in all directions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 684925.0,
      "end_time": 687555.0,
      "text": "radiating gardens"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 687580.0,
      "end_time": 689523.0,
      "text": "from each of the alcoves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 691277.0,
      "end_time": 692851.0,
      "text": "radiating paths."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 695970.0,
      "end_time": 699564.0,
      "text": "Last October, the opening ceremonies --"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 700666.0,
      "end_time": 703671.0,
      "text": "a beautiful, sacred event,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 704451.0,
      "end_time": 707478.0,
      "text": "5,000 people from 80 countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 707502.0,
      "end_time": 711415.0,
      "text": "a continuous river of visitors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 711439.0,
      "end_time": 714909.0,
      "text": "indigenous people from all over South America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 714933.0,
      "end_time": 717548.0,
      "text": "some who had never left their villages."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 719103.0,
      "end_time": 723601.0,
      "text": "And of course, that this temple belongs to people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 723625.0,
      "end_time": 729600.0,
      "text": "the collective, of many cultures and walks of life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 729840.0,
      "end_time": 730500.0,
      "text": "many beliefs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 730524.0,
      "end_time": 735137.0,
      "text": "and for me, what&#39;s most important is what it feels like on the inside;"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 735161.0,
      "end_time": 737987.0,
      "text": "that it feel intimate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 738110.0,
      "end_time": 739766.0,
      "text": "sacred,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 739790.0,
      "end_time": 742170.0,
      "text": "and that everyone is welcome."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 742194.0,
      "end_time": 746813.0,
      "text": "And if even a few who come"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 746837.0,
      "end_time": 750550.0,
      "text": "have the same reaction as that security guard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 751704.0,
      "end_time": 756930.0,
      "text": "then it truly would be their temple."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 757620.0,
      "end_time": 758663.0,
      "text": "And I would love that."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 758687.0,
      "end_time": 759861.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 759885.0,
      "end_time": 764982.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}